TITLE: Vanishing North Atlantic right whale to remain protected under Endangered Species Act
SUMMARY: The vanishing North Atlantic right whale will remain protected under the Endangered Species Act. The species will require a series of protective steps to ensure they don't go extinct.

TITLE: North Carolina crash during police pursuit kills 1, injures 1
SUMMARY: A car crash during a police pursuit in North Carolina killed one person and injured another. The chase involved a car linked to an armed robbery on Tuesday.

TITLE: Homeless man dies from the cold while traveling to see family members on Christmas day
SUMMARY: A homeless man died from cold weather exposure on Christmas day. The man was trying to travel from Louisiana to Tennessee to get to his family. He was living in the woods when he died.

TITLE: Suspected California serial killer charged with seventh murder
SUMMARY: Suspected serial killer Wesley Brownlee was linked to a seventh murder and is facing five additional charges in California after a rash of random attacks.

TITLE: In Alabama, Autauga County sheriff dies after short battle with cancer
SUMMARY: The Autauga County sheriff died on Monday after briefly battling cancer. He was weeks from starting his third term as sheriff. The governor will choose someone to take his place.

TITLE: Alabama teens arrested in drive-by shooting that killed 12-year-old
SUMMARY: Alabama teenagers were arrested in a drive-by shooting that killed a 12-year-old girl who was asleep in her home on Wednesday. The suspects fired 17 bullets inside the home.

TITLE: Jackson, Mississippi declares water emergency amid boil advisory
SUMMARY: A local state of emergency was declared in Jackson, Mississippi, after frigid wintry weather upended water systems in several southern over the past few days.

TITLE: Viral video shows Indianapolis woman driving car on frozen canal before going through the ice
SUMMARY: People are still stunned after witnessing a car driving on a frozen canal in downtown Indianapolis on Christmas night. Police have arrested the driver.

TITLE: Florida teens found dead with gunshot wounds in undeveloped subdivision, police hunt for clues
SUMMARY: An investigation is underway after two teenagers, ages 14 and 16, were found dead in southwest Palm Bay on Christmas night, the Palm Bay Police Department said.

TITLE: Idaho murders: Kaylee Goncalves' Range Rover retrieved from city lot
SUMMARY: Family lawyer Shanon Gray picked up slain University of Idaho student Kaylee Goncalves' silver Ranger Rover from Moscow, Idaho, police on Thursday, nearly six weeks after her murder.
